creator: Dealership for Life Mobile Apps
descriptionHtml:
The Kerry Rewards Mobile App is designed for customers of Program Benefits with locations in Florence KY. This app allows you to view and track your participation in the dealership's loyalty program and to view the service history of your vehicle. In addition, you are eligible for exclusive deals on service made available only to Mobile App Users!

Other features include:
Detailed Vehicle Specifications
Document Keeper
Recommended Maintenance
MPG Calculator
Parked Car Finder
QR Code and VIN Barcode scanner
New and pre-owned inventory
Contact the Dealership
Directions to Dealership
